NIGIDDEPOLK: <color=#C87D1DFF>When an opposing character is defeated:</color> Deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters.
<color=#C87D1DFF>After opposing characters take Elemental Reaction DMG:</color> Create 1 Omni Element. (Can be triggered up to 3 times per Round)

<color=#C87D1DFF>After your character uses a Skill:</color> Create an Ambuscade Mine of your character's Element on the opposing side of the field. The Ambuscade Mine will deal 1 DMG of that corresponding element to opposing reinforcements after they enter play.
<color=#C87D1DFF>When your character uses a Skill or equips a Talent:</color> Spend 1 less Elemental Die. (Can be triggered once per Round per character)
<color=#C87D1DFF>When your character uses a Charged Attack: </color>DMG dealt +1. Draw 1 card after finalization.
<color=#C87D1DFF>When your character equipped with both a Weapon and an Artifact uses a Skill:</color> Spend 3 less Elemental Dice. (Once per Round)
<color=#C87D1DFF>When an opposing character is defeated:</color> Draw 1 card. Your current active character deals +1 DMG in this match. (Can stack. Max 3 Stacks.)
<color=#C87D1DFF>When you play a Weapon or Artifact card with a cost of at least 3:</color> Spend 3 less Elemental Dice. (Once per Round)
